{"tid":493089,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樓市最悲情，20萬人賣自住樓等跌","createTime":"2017-12-08T07:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T19:03:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a71a0fe307ed4309f94a9ed36f6fd6cf298dd442","tid":493089,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/154143_11119ff938c9d34855d5a3548ec7411d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F154143_11119ff938c9d34855d5a3548ec7411d.jpg&h=5f276bb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓價持續攀升，花旗銀行公布2017年第3季市民置業意向調查，結果顯示，認為可用400萬港元以下置業的受訪者比例逐年遞減，由2012年的79%下跌至2017年的53%；有16%受訪者認為需800萬元或以上置業，為5年以來新高。 <br />\n<br />\n調查亦顯示，過去10年內推算有至少36萬港人「落錯車」，即在出售物業後沒有再次置業，當中有20萬人至今沒有任何物業。而其餘16萬人則本來擁有多於1個物業。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171207/photo/bkn-20171207110537204-1207_00842_001_02p.jpg?20171208050405\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171207110537204-1207_00842_001_02p.jpg%3F20171208050405&h=edaf7613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，有5%受訪者認為現時是置業好時機，較第2季低位的1%有所回升；認為現時並非置業好時機的受訪者，則按季下跌至68%，反映市民對置業取態回復進取。有8%表示「好有需要」於現時置業，推算約有37萬人。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171207/photo/bkn-20171207110537204-1207_00842_001_03p.jpg?20171208050405\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171207110537204-1207_00842_001_03p.jpg%3F20171208050405&h=6c8a1334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於對樓價看法，有5成半成受訪者認為於未來12個月會上升，按年增11%；11%受訪者認為樓價會於未來1年下跌，按年回落1成，反映市民未有看淡樓市走勢。 <br />\n<br />\n市民預期樓價易升難跌，有49%受訪者表示對置業興趣不大，但仍有21%受訪者表示有興趣置業，按季上升7%，是調查開展以來第2高位。 <br />\n─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171207/photo/bkn-20171207110537204-1207_00842_001_04p.jpg?20171208050405\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171207110537204-1207_00842_001_04p.jpg%3F20171208050405&h=5d922443&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3eb4d41a59158afd460b472a328287723fbc685","tid":493089,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:46:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171207/mobile/bkn-20171207110537204-1207_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171207%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171207110537204-1207_00842_001.html&d=UYGkvbzWySGVpgnXueqqfO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=76745023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171207/mobile/bkn-20171207110537204-1207_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cccdfb1287de2d0ef893f13f35fdbfd6b9561f45","tid":493089,"uid":98086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"「基數：全部受訪者」<br />\n咁同無講有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b79331f86a15af493c57df9ba70cb4c79a30e4","tid":493089,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead2440a14c64f057fb78ae85807cc67dc74f808","tid":493089,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541681217e14a0f9f018983fb78a806046fd7dff","tid":493089,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592c7f60b0bf075e770365c2d23bdab36caf3ffb","tid":493089,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T09:46:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab9e2b2a11e03f48795b9929a233daa1c7816df5","tid":493089,"uid":41508